Package: result
Title: Result Monad for Operations that can Fail
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Soumya", "Ray", , "soumya.ray@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre", "cph"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-7497-3281"))
Description: Provides Either/Result monad functions like Success() and Failure() 
    to capture the result of operations that can succeed of fail. Results can be
    bound together in chains of operations.
Encoding: UTF-8
